functions.name: delegate
functions.desc:
Ask a capable helper for help looking up a piece of information or performing an action.
Do not simply repeat what the user said as instructions.
You should use this to break up complex user queries into multiple simpler steps.
NOTE: Helpers cannot see previous parts of your conversation.

instructions.description: Detailed instructions on what your helper should do to help you.

msg.content: What are the record high temperatures in Celcius in the top 5 most populous cities in the world?
What are the record high temperatures in Celcius in the top 5 most populous cities in the world?

Here are the record high temperatures in the five most populous cities in the world:

- **Tokyo, Japan** — 39.5°C (103.1°F)
- **Delhi, India** — 49.2°C (120.6°F)
- **Shanghai, China** — 40.9°C (105.6°F)
- **São Paulo, Brazil** — 35.3°C (95.5°F)
- **Mexico City, Mexico** — 33.9°C (93°F)

The temperature in all these cities was recorded at different times. For instance, Tokyo's record high was registered on August 4, 2023, while Delhi's was recorded on June 10, 1952.
